<TD WIDTH=460 COLSPAN=2 VALIGN="TOP"><P><CENTER>
<a href="/product-info/powirtrain/pwrtrain.pdf">
<IMG SRC="/graphics/powertrain.gif" ALT="powIRtrain" WIDTH=276 HEIGHT=67></a></CENTER>
<P>Design Kits, integrated power stages, power modules, assemblies and HVIC
drivers are now available. The initial kits are the IRPT1053,
IRPT1056, IRPT2051 and IRPT5051 covering 1 to 15HP (0.75 to 11Kw).
 The design kits not only include the complete hardware for the
power stage of an AC motor drive; they also include the complete
design details for you to copy in whole or part. Operating instructions,
electrical schematic, bill of materials, mechanical layout, guidelines
for customizing the board layout, and even the Gerber files on
diskette are of course included.  Look for more Pow<I>IR</I>train<font size=-2><sup>TM</sup></font>
product family releases later in the year as detailed in the availability
matrix also included in the Design Kit.  Use the "Contact IR" button above
to contact the local Sales Rep or Sales Office in your area for Design Kit Sales
Information.
<BR>
<P>
We at International Rectifier are committed to being your partner
in business and providing you with the innovation and support
required in today's competitive global business environment. International
Rectifier's semiconductor products are built to the highest quality
standards, and over the last 50 years have achieved an outstanding
reputation for reliability. We are confident that you will find
this same level of quality and reliability in the Pow<I>IR</I>train<font size=-2><sup>TM</sup></font>
family of system solutions and products.<BR>
<P>
Thomas Kaporch<BR>
Director of Marketing, Motor Drives<P>
For more information, see the related Pow<I>IR</I>train<font size=-2><sup>TM</sup></font> article. 
